---
title: Pan-Fried Turkey Steak with Mushroom Sauce and Pancetta Roasties
description: There are many ways you can tenderise meat. Marinating is good. Hanging works especially well for game. In some parts of the world they like to wrap stuff in papaya leaves. But our method of choice today is whacking the daylights out of some turkey with a frying pan! Simple, effective and fun...
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-fried-turkey-steak-wk-41-d75b6983-e877851d.jpg
